Package com.lukas783.mdt.api

A group of interfaces and data POJOs to be implemented throughout the application.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IProcessServiceListener
    A listener interface that can be implemented by any class that needs to listen to the ProcessService singleton service.
    IUiServiceListener
    A listener interface that can be implemented by any class that needs to listen to the UiService singleton-service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MavenTask
    A POJO that defines a task to complete.
    MavenTask.Builder
    A Builder to force proper creation of the MavenTask object.
